name: Balloon Girl
description:
Balloon Girl meditates upon the hill with teddy in her arms and a hot air balloon held by a string in her hands. This image is inspired by books I was read to as a child and pictures i saw in fairy tales. Balloon Girl is also inspired by Japanese anime.

Description::

Balloon Girl is an original hand drawn illustration. It has been printed as a high quality archival print with Epson Ultrachrome Inks onto gorgeous Canson Aquarelle Rag Paper (240gsm). It features ink, pencil and digital colouring in.

I have signed the work personally and included an artist biography in the package.

The size is 30 x 42cm.

Each print is carefully packaged for weatherproofing and lined with cardboard to prevent bending.

Please note copyright remains with the artist.

Enjoy x
